\cf0 Before implementing any accommodation, it's vital for the team to adopt the right mindset. This involves embracing an "experimental mindset," recognizing that learning comes from trial and error. The guiding principle must be to "prioritize long term connection, autonomy, and nervous system support over compliance, skills, and expectations." These accommodations are not a simple checklist to be completed, but rather a dynamic set of tools in an ongoing, responsive process of building trust and safety.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

