\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 5.0 Crafting Meaningful and Measurable PDA-Friendly IEP Goals\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Traditional, compliance-based IEP goals are often inappropriate and counter-productive for PDA learners. Goals focused on task completion (e.g., "will complete 80% of worksheets") can become a source of demand and anxiety, leading to more avoidance. Instead, goals must be thoughtfully reframed to focus on building skills in areas that support the student's long-term well-being and independence, such as self-advocacy, emotional regulation, flexible thinking, and interoception.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 Applying the S.M.A.R.T. Framework Through a PDA-Friendly Lens\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 The S.M.A.R.T. (Specific, Measurable, Action Words, Realistic, Time-Limited) framework remains a valuable tool, but it must be applied with a neuroaffirming perspective.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Specific:
\f1\b0  The goal clearly states what the learner will achieve.\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Measurable:
\f1\b0  Progress can be tracked through criteria like frequency or accuracy, but should also include methods like student self-report and staff observation.\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Action Words:
\f1\b0  The language should be collaborative and empowering. Instead of "will follow," use phrases like "
\f0\b will communicate the need for
\f1\b0 ," "
\f0\b will partner with
\f1\b0 ," or "
\f0\b will use taught strategies
\f1\b0 ." This centers the student's agency.\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Realistic:
\f1\b0  This is the most critical adaptation. A "realistic" goal for a PDA learner must account for their 
\f0\b fluctuating capacity
\f1\b0 . Success should not be measured by consistent, linear progress but by their ability to use tools and strategies when they are regulated enough to do so.\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Time-Limited:
\f1\b0  A clear timeframe provides structure for the IEP team.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

